"languageCode":"pa","languageName":{"simpleText":"펀자브어"}},{"languageCode":"fo","languageName":{"simpleText":"페로어"}},{"languageCode":"fa","languageName":{"simpleText":"페르시아어"}},{"languageCode":"pt","languageName":{"simpleText":"포르투갈어"}},{"languageCode":"pt-PT","languageName":{"simpleText":"포르투갈어(포르투갈)"}},{"languageCode":"pl","languageName":{"simpleText":"폴란드어"}},{"languageCode":"fr","languageName":{"simpleText":"프랑스어"}},{"languageCode":"fj","languageName":{"simpleText":"피지어"}},{"languageCode":"fi","languageName":{"simpleText":"핀란드어"}},{"languageCode":"fil","languageName":{"simpleText":"필리핀어"}},{"languageCode":"haw","languageName":{"simpleText":"하와이어"}},{"languageCode":"ha","languageName":{"simpleText":"하우사어"}},{"languageCode":"ko","languageName":{"simpleText":"한국어"}},{"languageCode":"hu","languageName":{"simpleText":"헝가리어"}},{"languageCode":"bho","languageName":{"simpleText":"호즈푸리어"}},{"languageCode":"hmn","languageName":{"simpleText":"히몸어"}},{"languageCode":"iw","languageName":{"simpleText":"히브리어"}},{"languageCode":"hi","languageName":{"simpleText":"힌디어"}},{"languageCode":"kri","languageName":{"simpleText":"Kri"}}],"defaultAudioTrackIndex":1}},"videoDetails":{"videoId":"jWs7k3kGqgI","title":"우리나라 공학자들이 만들어낸 미친 신기술! 단 한방울의 물로 전기를 만들어버리다. (국뽕주의)","lengthSeconds":"346","keywords":["에스오디","과학","공학","SOD SCIENCE","김일두","카이스트","반도체","소름돋는이야기","과학이야기","KAIST","삼성","국뽕"],"channelId":"UCSPMRoAphbObUYeDaX367Fg","isOwnerViewing":false,"shortDescription":"다른게 국뽕이 아니라 이런 것이 진짜 국뽕이 아닐까요?\n맨날 한국이 세계를 놀래켜서 일본은 망하고 다른 선진국은 긴장하며 고개를 숙이는게 아니라요...\n\n카이스트의 김일두 교수님의 마인드가 정말 멋집니다.\n대한민국 기술을 응원합니다.\n\n흥미로우셨길.\n감사합니다.\n\n-  내용 출처\n1. 삼성 뉴스룸, “몇 방울의 물만으로 전기를?”, 2018 (http://me2.do/FirQGADd)\n2. Tae Gwang Yun et al, “Transpiration Driven Electrokinetic Power Generator”, ACS Nano, 2019\n3. Jaehyeong Bae et al, “Self-operating transpiration-driven electrokinetic power generator with an artificial hydrological cycle”, Energy \u0026 Environmental Science, 2019\n4. 카이스트 신소재공학과, “김일두 교수, 물 몇 방울로 전기 만들어내는 기술 개발”, 2019\n- BGM: Flying High, FREDJI","isCrawlable":true,"thumbnail":{"thumbnails":[{"url":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/jWs7k3kGqgI/hqdefault.jpg?sqp=-oaymwEiCKgBEF5IWvKriqkDFQgBFQAAAAAYASUAAMhCPQCAokN4AQ==\u0026rs=AOn4CLBeiV1L5pqxnp-rmCtR1jkxR3oGdQ","width":168,"height":94},{"url":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/jWs7k3kGqgI/hqdefault.jpg?sqp=-oaymwEiCMQBEG5IWvKriqkDFQgBFQAAAAAYASUAAMhCPQCAokN4AQ==\u0026rs=AOn4CLDeb6boATPiY5zxVRYvwcEPTALchw","width":196,"height":110},{"url":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/jWs7k3kGqgI/hqdefault.jpg?sqp=-oaymwEjCPYBEIoBSFryq4qpAxUIARUAAAAAGAElAADIQj0AgKJDeAE=\u0026rs=AOn4CLDSviYcnCLT0b5GkmuEEVUl9ZK5cQ","width":246,"height":138},{"url":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/jWs7k3kGqgI/hqdefault.jpg?sqp=-oaymwEjCNACELwBSFryq4qpAxUIARUAAAAAGAElAADIQj0AgKJDeAE=\u0026rs=AOn4CLCLRYerkpNeqixJLE3_HjpwN0K2Mw","width":336,"height":188},{"url":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/jWs7k3kGqgI/maxresdefault.jpg","width":1920,"height":1080}]},"allowRatings":true,"viewCount":"239750","author":"에스오디 SOD","isPrivate":false,"isUnpluggedCorpus":false,"isLiveContent":false,"isTvfilmVideo":false},"annotations":[{"playerAnnotationsExpandedRenderer":{"featuredChannel":{"startTimeMs":"0","endTimeMs":"325000","watermark":{"thumbnails":[{"url":"https://i.ytimg.com/an/SPMRoAphbObUYeDaX367Fg/featured_channel.jpg?v=65083358","width":40,"height":40}]},"trackingParams":"CBEQ8zciEwif7NO2xpKTAxXUBeoBHUhAH9Y=","navigationEndpoint":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBEQ8zciEwif7NO2xpKTAxXUBeoBHUhAH9YyAml2ygEEwxOPRQ==","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"/channel/UCSPMRoAphbObUYeDaX367Fg","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_CHANNEL","rootVe":3611,"apiUrl":"/youtubei/v1/browse"}},"browseEndpoint":{"browseId":"UCSPMRoAphbObUYeDaX367Fg"}},"channelName":"에스오디 SOD","subscribeButton":{"subscribeButtonRenderer":{"buttonText":{"runs":[{"text":"구독"}]},"subscribed":false,"enabled":true,"type":"FREE","channelId":"UCSPMRoAphbObUYeDaX367Fg","showPreferences":false,"subscribedButtonText":{"runs":[{"text":"구독중"}]},"unsubscri