cription","visibility":"ENGAGEMENT_PANEL_VISIBILITY_EXPANDED"}},{"clickTrackingParams":"CJMCEM2rARgBIhMI-f_TtsaSkwMVhUA4BR0MgAtRygEEwxOPRQ==","scrollToEngagementPanelCommand":{"targetId":"engagement-panel-structured-description"}}]}},"showLessCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CJMCEM2rARgBIhMI-f_TtsaSkwMVhUA4BR0MgAtRygEEwxOPRQ==","changeEngagementPanelVisibilityAction":{"targetId":"engagement-panel-structured-description","visibility":"ENGAGEMENT_PANEL_VISIBILITY_HIDDEN"}},"attributedDescription":{"content":"다른게 국뽕이 아니라 이런 것이 진짜 국뽕이 아닐까요?\n맨날 한국이 세계를 놀래켜서 일본은 망하고 다른 선진국은 긴장하며 고개를 숙이는게 아니라요...\n\n카이스트의 김일두 교수님의 마인드가 정말 멋집니다.\n대한민국 기술을 응원합니다.\n\n흥미로우셨길.\n감사합니다.\n\n내용 출처\n1. 삼성 뉴스룸, “몇 방울의 물만으로 전기를?”, 2018 (http://me2.do/FirQGADd)\n2. Tae Gwang Yun et al, “Transpiration Driven Electrokinetic Power Generator”, ACS Nano, 2019\n3. Jaehyeong Bae et al, “Self-operating transpiration-driven electrokinetic power generator with an artificial hydrological cycle”, Energy \u0026 Environmental Science, 2019\n4. 카이스트 신소재공학과, “김일두 교수, 물 몇 방울로 전기 만들어내는 기술 개발”, 2019\nBGM: Flying High, FREDJI","commandRuns":[{"startIndex":190,"length":22,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CJMCEM2rARgBIhMI-f_TtsaSkwMVhUA4BR0MgAtRSILUmsi38s61jQHKAQTDE49F","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqazNWc1RLUU50VHFUd3ZMNWRhQmhTS1FkX21VUXxBQ3Jtc0ttem8tSXRpYmhiWDRFTGNtS0psTDQ2Nk1KSEppQjVTYXVqS1BIWjVpZVFsYWFmSVdSb0laVXlDdTBxTWlQb2Z5bjhrZDVsdnNtVjQ5TVE1dkY2YVR0VXJSNEdadFBOS25LVkZVWlFOMjhlbXk4eXdWRQ\u0026q=http%3A%2F%2Fme2.do%2FFirQGADd\u0026v=jWs7k3kGqgI","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_UNKNOWN","rootVe":83769}},"urlEndpoint":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqazNWc1RLUU50VHFUd3ZMNWRhQmhTS1FkX21VUXxBQ3Jtc0ttem8tSXRpYmhiWDRFTGNtS0psTDQ2Nk1KSEppQjVTYXVqS1BIWjVpZVFsYWFmSVdSb0laVXlDdTBxTWlQb2Z5bjhrZDVsdnNtVjQ5TVE1dkY2YVR0VXJSNEdadFBOS25LVkZVWlFOMjhlbXk4eXdWRQ\u00